Package io.github.zero88.jooqx.adapter

Provides the classes and interfaces to adapt and covert the Vert.x SQL result set to jOOQ record
Since:
1.0.0
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RowConverterStrategy<R,​I>
    A row converter strategy collects each row in result set to an expectation result
    SQLResultAdapter<T,​R>
    SQL Result adapter receives Result set then mapping to expected result
    SQLResultAdapter.SQLResultListAdapter<T,​R>
    Indicates select many row
    SQLResultAdapter.SQLResultOneAdapter<T,​R>
    Indicates select only one row
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SelectAdhocListResult<T extends org.jooq.TableLike<? extends org.jooq.Record>,​R>
    Select Adhoc adapter for list result is a base class for custom Select list implementations in client code.
    SelectAdhocOneResult<T extends org.jooq.TableLike<? extends org.jooq.Record>,​R>
    Select Adhoc adapter for one result is a base class for custom Select one implementations in client code.
    SelectCount
    Select count result adapter that defines output in Integer type
    SelectExists
    Select exists result adapter that defines output in Boolean type
    SelectList<T extends org.jooq.TableLike<? extends org.jooq.Record>,​R extends org.jooq.Record,​I>
    Select list result adapter that returns list of output
    SelectOne<T extends org.jooq.TableLike<? extends org.jooq.Record>,​R extends org.jooq.Record,​I>
    Select one result adapter that returns only one row
    SQLCollectorPart<R extends org.jooq.Record,​I>
    SQL collector part that helps to create collector in RowConverterStrategy.createCollector(Function)
    SQLCollectorPart.IdentityCollectorPart<R extends org.jooq.Record>  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SelectStrategy
    Represents for strategy when handling result set
